{"_id":"bUSftDdIxjl1Bgb3","name":"Voleur","permission":{"default":0,"2iWYjvpZCb5uRmvI":3},"type":"profession","data":{"description":"","source":"ARIA","key":"voleur","competences":[{"_id":"ylU3eFFrYe4xpCaw","name":"Oreilles opportunes","permission":{"default":0,"jMtEYjQyz5Ted7Cb":3},"type":"competence","data":{"description":"<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Vous &ecirc;tes au courant des rumeurs les plus pointues sur un sujet pr&eacute;cis. </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Une fois par jour, vous pouvez demander &agrave; votre MJ des renseignements sur un th&egrave;me sp&eacute;cifique et ce dernier doit vous transmettre les &eacute;l&eacute;ments le concernant, &agrave; l&rsquo;exception des points identifi&eacute;s comme secrets. </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Vous savez en outre quelles sont les rumeurs les plus fond&eacute;es.</span></p>","source":"","key":"oreilles-opportunes","special":true,"language":false,"link1":"","link2":"","score":null},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.aria.competencesspepretire.ylU3eFFrYe4xpCaw"}},"img":"systems/aria/ui/icons/competences/capacitiesSpecial.webp","effects":[]}]},"flags":{},"img":"/systems/aria/ui/icons/professions/profession.webp","effects":[]}
